# What Cloudflare Workers uploads/serves as static assets — separate from
# .gitignore, which only controls what git tracks. wrangler.jsonc's assets
# directory is "./" (the whole project root), so without this file EVERYTHING
# here — including .git internals and node_modules — is publicly fetchable
# at the live URL. Confirmed and fixed 2026-07-16 after .git/config turned
# out to be genuinely reachable at the deployed site.
.git/
.gitignore
.assetsignore
node_modules/
node_modules/**
node_modules/.*
package.json
package-lock.json
README.md
wrangler.jsonc
scripts/
